General.Name: Cell Impact AB
General.Description: Cell Impact AB (publ) engages in manufacture and sale of bipolar flow plates for hydrogen fuel cells in Sweden, Europe, North America, Asia, and internationally. The company offers plates with and precise flow patterns. It serves hydrogen fuel cells producers. The company was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Karlskoga, Sweden.
